==English==

===Etymology===
Russian [[самиздат]] (''samizdat'') "self-published", from [[сам]] (''sam'') "self" + ''издат'' (''izdat’''), truncation of [[издательство]] (''izdatjel’stvo'') "publishing house".  Compare [[Госиздат]] (''Gosizdat'').

